ReconciliationCommentForm is a Form
    use for action UpdateComment
    title is "ReconciliationComment"
    Layout
        two column
            CashManagementAccount
                display as text
            CashManagementAccount.Title
                no label
                display as text
        two column
            LineMatchField
                display as text
            ReconciledAmount
                display as text
        single column
            Comment
                use text area of 2 lines
